name: Seal Dog
description: Seal Dog is a meme token featuring a playful dog disguised as a seal, blending humour and creativity with blockchain technology. Built on the SUI blockchain, Seal Dog fosters a vibrant community focused on fun and engagement. With a commitment to decentralization, innovation, and laughter, it aims to become a symbol of joy and inclusivity in the crypto space. The project also explores unique utilities for community-driven growth.
